Package: periodicDNA
Type: Package
Title: Probing DNA sequences for periodic oligonucleotides
Version: 0.2.1
Date: 2020-03-04
Encoding: UTF-8
Author: Jacques Serizay
Maintainer: Jacques Serizay <jacquesserizay@gmail.com>
Description: The functions in this package provide a straightforward approach 
    to identify periodic occurrences of k-mers or oligonucleotides in longer sequences such as regulatory 
    elements. 
URL: www.github.com/js2264/periodicDNA
